# Write the Voice Role and Durability ADR

## Question

Write the ADR that makes this effort's boundary moves official, knowingly superseding `roles/voice.md` and ADR-0178 (blocked on recovering 0178's text — you don't supersede a contract you can't read). It records: the expanded write scopes (voice appends decisions, creates/claims/resolves tracker tickets, and kicks off jobs/research; it never edits code or runs arbitrary commands), the OpenRouter exception for the voice loop (repo rule bans it elsewhere; Joel approved it for this use case 2026-07-11), the LiveKit Cloud media-plane decision and why self-hosted k8s never returns, and the new durability contract — missed-call paging, registration canary, synthetic daily call, answer-depends-only-on-LiveKit+LLM, per-turn persistence, Inngest at-least-once post-call processing, and boot verification. Lands in the joelclaw ADR corpus wherever the recovered Vault decisions settle.
